org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface IDynamicAccessNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IBinaryOperatorNode, IExpressionNode, IOperatorNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicAccessNode

    public interface IDynamicAccessNode
extends IBinaryOperatorNode
    An AST node representing the dynamic-access ("[]") binary operator.

    The typical shape of this node is: 

     IDynamicAccessNode 
   IExpressionNode <-- getLeftOperandNode()
   IExpressionNode <-- getRightOperandNode()
    For example, a[i] is represented as 
     IDynamicAccessNode "[]"
   IIdentifierNode "a"
   IIdentiferNode "i"
